attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Carolyn Riley RL. Est. Srvcs, Inc.

data.description: Calling all investors! Must see home with beautiful hard wood floors throughout. Minutes from The University of Akron, downtown, and other amenities. This home offers a dining room just off the kitchen and a large living room with a fireplace. There are 3 bedrooms and one bath (bathtub and separate walk in shower) on the second floor. Full basement for plenty of storage and laundry. Big front porch to sit outside on and relax. One car detached garage. Nice quiet backyard. Do not miss out on this fantastic investment property. Schedule your private showing today.
